comment: pttrns has just about every UI design you could imagine, all within easy acess.
Visiting this site every week is like Christmas, new and high quality surprises.
I hope HTML5 UP expands because I really like the free content.
Abduzeedo has a really great content and lots of inspiration. I also use the site to browse tutorials on how to do website mockups and make the websites.
Abudzeedo finds the best website content. I highly recommend people check it out.
ThemeForest has great themes. I use them for personal projects then tweak them to suit my needs.
HTML5 UP has great free templates.
If you're looking to make better UI for your next mobile app, look no further than pttrns.
Creative Market has free content every week. It's great to use for personal projects.
Creative Market is a great community of designers that post high quality website templates for sale
Pinterest has so much content, it's great to get some inspiration for anything web or mobile design.
I like that I can use Pinterest to collect all the inspirational things I see on the web about design.
